{% comment %}
  snippets/header-menu-item.liquid
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Dispatcher — reads block.type and renders the correct sub-snippet.

  This is the single composability seam in the menu system:
    - Add a new block type → add one sub-snippet + one branch here.
    - Swap a sub-snippet → everything else stays untouched.

  VARIABLES (passed from snippets/header-menu.liquid):
    block  {block object}  — one item from section.blocks.
                             block.type is the routing key.
                             block.settings holds all merchant inputs.

  BLOCK TYPES → SUB-SNIPPETS:
    link      → header-menu-item--link.liquid
    linklist  → header-menu-item--linklist.liquid
    mega      → header-menu-item--mega.liquid
    promo     → header-menu-item--promo.liquid
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
{% endcomment %}

{%- case block.type -%}

  {%- when 'link' -%}
    {%- render 'header-menu-item--link', block: block -%}

  {%- when 'linklist' -%}
    {%- render 'header-menu-item--linklist', block: block -%}

  {%- when 'mega' -%}
    {%- render 'header-menu-item--mega', block: block -%}

  {%- when 'promo' -%}
    {%- render 'header-menu-item--promo', block: block -%}

{%- endcase -%}
